{"tid":1430212,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"［建議］有關正負皮","createTime":"2019-08-07T16:33:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T21:01:35.000Z","uid":167973,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b084f60ed2211c64358a6e0b32c7877b39db8103","tid":1430212,"uid":167973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:33:42.000Z","msg":"依家延遲顯示正負皮<br />\n雖然係有助獨立思考 防止三毛帶風向<br />\n但係有時有啲po係好即時 突發 或者快閃<br />\n尤其係依家個熱門 半個鐘就唔同樣<br />\n真係需要正負皮嚟睇返即時認受性 或者有幾多人留意到個po<br />\n<br />\n所以我建議<br />\nFor會員：當你撳完正負皮之後 你就可以見到依家嘅正負皮 未撳就睇唔到 或者可以選擇「顯示正負皮」 但係撳咗之後就無得再投返正負皮<br />\n<br />\nFor cd-rom: 本身隱藏正負皮 可以撳「顯示正負皮 」<br />\n<br />\n希望連仔考慮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nP.S.連仔好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b2482222a87301dc2c5c2c2ae22436112df3a53","tid":1430212,"uid":2562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:37:43.000Z","msg":"幫手文宣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係會唔夠人！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hmQcRzv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhmQcRzv.jpg&h=7f5efe94&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s8rvDew.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs8rvDew.jpg&h=671c6067&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RAYFf1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRAYFf1c.jpg&h=d7384709&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0b0119f653605078ce5c25f2857807700a0f84e","tid":1430212,"uid":167973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:00:27.000Z","msg":"同埋（以下內容純屬9up)<br />\n我建議加一個類似「閱」嘅制<br />\n<br />\n例如話有啲資訊性強嘅 可以唔表態但係表示睇咗<br />\n<br />\n或者 有啲行動po 唔想決定住 睇定啲先 就可以撳 如果多人表示「閱」就即係要再detail啲 <br />\n<br />\n又或者今日 林鄭落區扮嘢 <br />\n我想俾負皮 鬧林鄭<br />\n又想俾正皮 讚樓主分析同發現到 表示認同<br />\n有時都唔知正好定負好 就會跟大隊<br />\n<br />\n其實我相信大家意思一樣 就係鬧林鄭<br />\n但係就會變成邊面多人撳邊面<br />\n如果有「閱」我應該會撳<br />\n<br />\n所以可以<br />\n正皮 xx 負皮yy 閱zz"},{"pid":"7f237c70d804a5fbfbbda94cce70514736aa65cd","tid":1430212,"uid":167330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:00:52.000Z","msg":"呢個idea掂喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但啲cd rom點算？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6783720c9b1f60e33553a289c319dd6218df1df4","tid":1430212,"uid":167330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:02:28.000Z","msg":"一係融合晒兩樣野<br />\n<br />\n照樣過某段時間可以睇到票數，但投咗票可以預先、即刻睇到"},{"pid":"083f89fa7f7cb12ab230c306e1925ec929b40da4","tid":1430212,"uid":167973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f237c70d804a5fbfbbda94cce70514736aa65cd","tid":1430212,"uid":167330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:00:52.000Z","msg":"呢個idea掂喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但啲cd rom點算？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:09:47.000Z","msg":"Cd rom 咪睇完上文之後<br />\n到平時睇正負皮個位<br />\n有個「顯示正負皮」嘅制<br />\n鍾意咪撳 唔鍾意咪唔撳<br />\n<br />\n其實今次個推遲顯示正負皮政策<br />\n都係想人有獨立思考 <br />\n唔好一眼就望落正負皮<br />\n再用既定立場去睇<br />\n所以有個撳遮一遮 諗一諗<br />\n我覺得都夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然 如果個cd rom 眼都唔眨就撳落去 <br />\n然後跟風嘅話 <br />\n都無辦法 <br />\n我哋無可能逼佢思考 最多係提醒下"},{"pid":"eab2e5164b719e56cf4880f63e39af6801748002","tid":1430212,"uid":167973,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6783720c9b1f60e33553a289c319dd6218df1df4","tid":1430212,"uid":167330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:02:28.000Z","msg":"一係融合晒兩樣野<br />\n<br />\n照樣過某段時間可以睇到票數，但投咗票可以預先、即刻睇到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:14:01.000Z","msg":"都得<br />\n或者可以有個「顯示正負皮」掣<br />\n其實我個idea都係好初步<br />\n拋個波出嚟大家討論下"},{"pid":"c5b09455a4e2281071a115ff80f23ffb6b280bbd","tid":1430212,"uid":80303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b084f60ed2211c64358a6e0b32c7877b39db8103","tid":1430212,"uid":167973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:33:42.000Z","msg":"依家延遲顯示正負皮<br />\n雖然係有助獨立思考 防止三毛帶風向<br />\n但係有時有啲po係好即時 突發 或者快閃<br />\n尤其係依家個熱門 半個鐘就唔同樣<br />\n真係需要正負皮嚟睇返即時認受性 或者有幾多人留意到個po<br />\n<br />\n所以我建議<br />\nFor會員：當你撳完正負皮之後 你就可以見到依家嘅正負皮 未撳就睇唔到 或者可以選擇「顯示正負皮」 但係撳咗之後就無得再投返正負皮<br />\n<br />\nFor cd-rom: 本身隱藏正負皮 可以撳「顯示正負皮 」<br />\n<br />\n希望連仔考慮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nP.S.連仔好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T20:25:13.000Z","msg":"&quot;幾多人留意到個po&quot; 可以顯示正負評總量<br />\n唔需要顯示評價本身"},{"pid":"64d1748af3f506f4ea3a9606e5d8fe16d0671d71","tid":1430212,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T21:01:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}